# ───────────────────────────── Build output ─────────────────────────────
bin/
obj/
[Dd]ebug/
[Rr]elease/
artifacts/
*.dll
*.pdb

# ──────────────────────── Secrets / sensitive config ─────────────────────
# Exchange API keys and any other credentials must NEVER be committed. The
# committed appsettings.json files carry blank placeholders only; real keys go
# in *.Secrets.json (or env vars) which stay local. These patterns are repo-wide
# so they cover the console app and any future project.
**/appsettings.Secrets.json
**/appsettings.*.Secrets.json
**/secrets.json
**/*.secrets.json
**/secrets.*.json

# Environment / dotenv files
.env
.env.*
*.env

# .NET user-secrets (if ever stored in-tree)
**/usersecrets.json

# Certificates / private keys
*.pfx
*.p12
*.pem
*.key
*.crt
*.cer

# ───────────────────────────── IDE / OS ─────────────────────────────────
.vs/
.idea/
.vscode/
*.user
*.suo
*.DotSettings.user
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
